{"tid":1640861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休息撚出黎反抗未？","createTime":"2019-10-09T06:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T07:14:36.000Z","uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93f38d988c0502af282bdff165b8c8850b778493","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"係張床度叫反抗？<br />\n等美國國會就唔駛做野？<br />\n過左人權民主法案就做乜都得？<br />\n<br />\n出黎啦 香港人 反抗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港<br />\n裝修紅資 懲罰黃絲</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4d65179687391aa8a5d6bac95bb3635e5dcc849c","tid":1640861,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"719629b669fb22be68e0df14523f04438fbf27cb","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:00:03.000Z","msg":"反抗"},{"pid":"eb83f66fe7b954c109d305b4e18eeb8fcafeb3f7","tid":1640861,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLCPmok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLCPmok.jpg&h=d80cc8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話要爭取國際線支持，我依家開左個英文版連儂牆啦，全部同我入去瘋狂貼文宣!<br />\n<br />\n[English] LIHKG Lennon Wall ver 1.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640768\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640768</a>"},{"pid":"bf6cb0a4d15b69257db3dc13e98b15bf5784adf0","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:01:05.000Z","msg":"18區 區區有樂"},{"pid":"c8596e035e5a87de8a2d2d1324e60380e92fb08e","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"區區開伙"},{"pid":"29c8867ab697c4059ea959e1f7110f1067157191","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.tvb.com/ti_img/mcm/267/57561d560d03c_1465261398.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.tvb.com%2Fti_img%2Fmcm%2F267%2F57561d560d03c_1465261398.jpg&h=f2238307&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a72a7da6a0f7a186024083f1226476e6fd04c5a","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"裝修又好 獅鳥又好 請對準春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dca5703d20cf6e0bfcf2924d0b58a08430d8dff","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"勇武咪去裝修 和理非咪去裝飾 休息撚咪去罷買 有錢撚咪去懲罰"},{"pid":"0816474dee21ae5374078493806c221b0b0f91b0","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"反抗喇 做撚左電狗呀？"},{"pid":"93661d513b269d8194cb752b0597eadab36d6d5e","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:08:22.000Z","msg":"電狗實驗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/en2krjz.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fen2krjz.amp&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ1UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=dffa82a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/en2krjz.amp</a>"},{"pid":"33355a6a0353536cfe608cff0b254ab60274c0db","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"1967年，美國心理學家塞利做了一個關於狗的實驗。<br />\n<br />\n他起初把狗關在籠子裏，只要蜂音器一響，就給狗施加難以忍受的電擊。於是被關在籠子裏的狗就被電得四處狂奔，屎滾尿流，驚恐哀叫，卻又無法逃出籠子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/i2.kknews.cc/SIG=cdcb9i/1p6r00034pn860o9p341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dcdcb9i%2F1p6r00034pn860o9p341.jpg&h=7395e3e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多次實驗後，只要蜂音器一響，狗就趴在地上驚恐哀叫，卻再也不狂奔了。<br />\n<br />\n後來，塞利就在電擊前先把籠門打開。但此時狗不但不逃，而是還沒等電擊出現呢，就倒地呻吟和顫抖。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼它們會這樣，連「狂奔，屎滾尿流，驚恐哀叫」，這些本能都沒有了呢？因為它們已經知道，那些是無用的。也就是說，反覆對動物施以無可逃避的強烈電擊會造成無助和絕望情緒。<br />\n<br />\n它本來可以主動逃避，卻只會絕望地等待痛苦的來臨，這就是「習得性無助」。<br />\n<br />\n這個詞很重要，在人身上也會出現，所以請先記住。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/i2.kknews.cc/SIG=bio0bu/1p680005s0q43523qn85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dbio0bu%2F1p680005s0q43523qn85.jpg&h=4d51c8f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼<br />\n<br />\n後來，賓州大學的馬丁˙賽利格曼又加強了這個實驗。<br />\n<br />\n他把狗分為兩組，分別放進一個籠子。這個籠子由兩部分構成，中間用隔板隔開，隔板的高度是狗可以輕易跳過去的。隔板的一邊有電擊，另一邊沒有電擊。<br />\n<br />\n當把經過前面實驗的狗放進這個籠子時，實驗者發現它們除了在頭半分鐘驚恐一陣子之外，此後一直卧倒在地接受電擊的痛苦，那麼容易逃脫的環境，它們連試也不去試一下。<br />\n<br />\n而當他把對照組中沒有經歷過電擊的狗放進有隔板的籠子裏以後，卻發現他們全部能逃脫電擊之苦，輕而易舉地從有電擊的一邊跳到安全的另一邊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2h0d664/1p6n000485234o8078q4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2h0d664%2F1p6n000485234o8078q4.jpg&h=54cbee48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個實驗所產生的現象，在心理學上稱之為「習得性無助」。後來有很多學者採用其它動物進行重複實驗，均得到了與上面相同的結果。<br />\n<br />\n」<br />\n<br />\n如果我們觀察現實生活中的那些長期經歷失敗的兒童，失去信心的員工，久病纏身的患者，會發現他們也會出現習得性無助的特徵。事實上，當一個人發現無論他如何努力，無論他幹什麼，都以失敗而告終時，他會覺得他控制不了整個局面，於是，他的精神支柱就會瓦解，鬥志也喪失了，最終會放棄一切努力，並陷入絕望的心境之中。"},{"pid":"6d16c3cad2af813b631e56bd7c0a8ae719752037","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:13:59.000Z","msg":"拆鋪某程度就係我地係習得性無助中 其中一樣比較比到成功咁既方法 係突破絕望既出路"},{"pid":"05d901e0035fd1ac9be231bb68cd31bd75305655","tid":1640861,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"反抗"}]}